    Wow, I really can't say enough great things about Love & Laughter Daycare, Sunnyvale. Ms. Nita and her Staff are amazing. My daughter started there 6 months ago when she was 17 months old. While she was there I always knew she was in excellent hands, I was never worried. Ms. Nita and her staff are always so caring, professional  and very attuned to each child's individual needs and habits. Not only did they help to foster my daughter's social growth but her academic growth as.There's always fun, supervised learning activities to do: painting, reading, singing, outing.
    %br
    Apart from the activities, every child gets variety of freshly prepared home food, fruits and lots of snacks which my daughter enjoys.Ms. Nita and her staff make sure that every child is fed and tries to cater every child's need.
    On a daily basis, when I pick up my daughter, Nita takes the time to tell me patiently the activities of the day, what our daughter has learned, what new things she's doing, and also what bad habits she's displaying so we can address it.
    An absolute must if you're looking for a safe, clean, loving, learning environment/home for your little one.
